Author: mechkladenets
Title: [ANN][SALE IS LIVE] GraphGrail Ai ‚Äì AI platform for Blockchain
Body: [TGE] GraphGrailAi announces the extension of the Token Sale.  We have decided to extend the Token Sale until May 25, 2018. The additional time is necessary for us to present to the investors our latest achievements on the project RoadShow.  Product.  1. We are announcing the Alpha release of the Data Markup Component for the Blockchain - one of the 3 key components of the platform!  Get access: https://labelapp.graphgrail.com  Log in, upload the data and order a markup. One can load data into the markup service via the application, set the cost of the work in GAI Tokens, indicate the semantic categories important for the business‚Äô tasks, consolidate the smart contract into the Rinkeby test network, and distribute the tasks to the employees. The markers will be able to perform tasks on the markup in our special Telegram and receive tokens in return. The result is that you get a ready-made database, suitable for training a neural network and automating the processing of business task data.  Read more about how the smart contract works in the previous announcement: https://medium.com/graphgrailai/graphgrail-ai-presents-its-smart-contract-f61f3eefe1d7  We are also announcing a series of ready-to-use APIs (application programming interface) - to be released on April 12: 1) Named Entity Recognition API in 6 languages (English, Chinese, German, French, Korean, Russian) with the ability to automatically identify key objects in the text. (Locations: cities, countries, regions, continents, neighborhoods, administrative divisions. Organizations: sports teams, newspapers, banks, universities, schools, non-profits, companies. Persons: politicians, scientists, artists, athletes). 2) Word embeddings in 6 languages as vector representations of words to determine proximity and identify semantic and syntactic features of words. Algorithms word2vec, doc2vec. A common way to examine space capturing via the embeddings is to query for the nearest neighbors of any word. 3) A ready-made API for identifying critical problems in a mobile game (150 million downloads, Google Play, App Store): including automatic categorization on Combat balance, Internet issues, Matchmaking, Bugs, Gameplay Balance, Graphics issues. The solution also takes into account the linguistic features of the data, such as slang and jargon of children from 8 to 15 years old.  All APIs will be available via URL in the form https://api.graphgrail.com/ner/v1/your_text  Marketing.  We have strengthened the Marketing component: 1. Twitter and working with opinion leaders. The project‚Äôs promotion on Twitter will now be conducted in a more integrated way, as we will use key information guides and leaders of the artificial intelligence industry to cover the activities of the GraphGrail Ai project. 2. Also, the additional time for the TGE will be required to neutralize the strong downtrend of the cryptocurrency market. 3. Negotiations have also started on listing the GAI Tokens on 2 crypto-exchanges. 4. RoadShow. An agreed travel plan was drawn up to attract large investors and crypto funds: Russia: April 12-13 http://demoday.south-itpark.ru/ Annual conference of start-ups and investors, 100+ participants, 20+ investors UAE: April 15-16 - http://www.terrapinn.com/exhibition/seamless-middle-east/index.stm 16-17 April - https://dubai.keynote.ae/ China, Hong Kong: April 18-19 - https://theinnovationenterprise.com/summits/big-data-analytics-hong-kong-2018/schedule?utm_source=Fintech+News&utm_medium=Email&utm_campaign=BDA+HK+2018 Singapore: April 26 - https://www.thecryptoeconomy.com/singapore/ UAE: May 2-3 - https://www.futureblockchainsummit.com/    Parameters of the TGE.  1. The TGE is extended until May 25, 2018 (+1 month and 10 days). 2. The Hardcap is reduced to $10M (Softcap remains the same). 3. The maximum amount of tokens sold at the TGE is also reduced from 120M to 100M. 4. The percentage of token distribution remains the same. 5. x2 token bonus for Presale investors ‚Äì remains the same.  All of the announced activities related to the product, the roadshows and marketing have been made after taking into account the interests of the investors and for presenting a good product on the market.  We at the GraphGrailAi team will continue to inform you to increase the transparency of our activities for all community members, including public reporting and development progress.  The GraphGrailAi team will keep you updated of our progress.

Author: alexvilis
Title: [ANN][SALE IS LIVE] GraphGrail Ai ‚Äì AI platform for Blockchain
Body: Working Case on Analysis of Data for Business and Determination of Purchase Probability  GraphGrail Ai, the world‚Äôs first Artificial Intelligence platform for Blockchain built on top of Natural Language Understanding technology with the DApps marketplace has created an application aimed at automating markup of text data and categorization for custom tasks. The application is capable of conducting analysis of the syntax and morphology of texts for the purpose of their semantic classification and subsequent determination of their application in business processes.  The case and its application was designed specifically for video hosting owners as such users are interested in the popularity of videos being reeled at specific timeframes.  Video hosting masters are in need of such applications as they are necessary for ensuring balance of various video topics on video hostings. Variety ensures that the masters of hostings receive earnings from selling advertisements of such videos. A lack of advertisements would mean lost traffic and revenues, while a lack of variety on channels would result in loss of audiences to other channels.  GraphGrail Ai has come up with a solution to the issue through the development of specialized interfaces, which allow for compilation of solutions for segmenting videos depending on the textual headlines of videos by topic. Thus, information is provided on more popular topics, both its video hosting and the hosting of competitors. As a result, potential imbalances in certain topics are identified, thus helping to adjust media policies of resources, thereby increasing profitability.  The function of automated monitoring of the activities of competitive hostings is of critical importance as it negates the necessity of manual control and adjustment of proprietary resources. As such, video hosting masters receive a powerful tool capable of maximizing their capitalization through the application of automated solutions based on AI and neural networks.  GraphGrail Ai is among the leading organizations in the field of neural machine learning and Artificial Intelligence development for application in textual formats through the use of Natural Language Learning technologies. The applications developed by GraphGrail Ai are some of the most comprehensive on the market and outstrip prominent brand names in their advanced nature and convenience of use in real world business environments.  https://medium.com/graphgrailai/working-case-on-analysis-of-data-for-business-and-determination-of-purchase-probability-c7bf0936483e

Author: Sombra De La Luna
Title: [ANN][SALE IS LIVE] GraphGrail Ai ‚Äì AI platform for Blockchain
Body: GraphGrailAi ICO is shifted to February 15, 2018. Cap is $2-$12M #ann #graphgrailai  As expected, GraphGrailAi ICO is to begin December 2017, but now crowdsale is shifted to February 15, 2018. According to Viktor Nosko, project founder, the decision to postpone ICO is currently related to taking a series of strategic steps for project promotion:  Why have we made decision to shift the ICO date?  Large investors are known to contribute up to half of funds in ICO. We take care of our investors. Cap to raise was significantly lowered to make ICO more attractive. It is very important thing - assuming super more than 2x Ethereum price growth ($700, compared to $300 in October). We will solve this in a very pleasure way both for early investors and for main ICO with the purpose to offer good profit, compared to Ethereum investment.  New ICO Cap is $2-$12M. Dates: 15 Feb - 15 Mar, 2018  First of all, we want to run crowdsale with the ready-to-use product. The main reason for that is the team integrity. What we focus at is to demonstrate traction, work of the running system, and not to raise ICO funds, like other teams having no up and running product. This will make our blockchain product look better and gain competitive edge over the teams that start ICO without any product.  Second, since the team launches ICO with the product at hand, GAI token will grow (expected). The other reason for that is that our platform will already have interested users, and we will be able to segment them. The product that already has any user base, even though these are potential users, the people, who want to try the product right after it is released, always confirms the business-model. Therefore, the user base will continue growing after ICO as well.  Third, there are too many ICOs per month available now in the blockchain market. Therefore, GraphGrailAi is bound to win against a great variety of projects to avoid spreading the funds across all projects and to have our project at least reach soft/ hard cap.  And, fourth, in our opinion, a key to successful ICO is PR abroad that includes business trips to foreign crypto conferences. To reach the fundraising goal of several millions USD we must build strong investment relations. To introduce our project and its founder to investors, to enhance trust to the project, we need to attend foreign conferences such as BlockShow Asia, etc.  More updates are coming soon. Next article will be about our progress.

Author: mechkladenets
Title: [ANN][SALE IS LIVE] GraphGrail Ai ‚Äì AI platform for Blockchain
Body: TOKENSALE STARTS ON the 19th of February  JOIN US    Site WhitePaper EN  WhitePaper RU  Telegram EN   Telegram RU   Steemit blog  Golos.io blog   Twitter    Introducing GraphGrail Ai ‚Äì the world‚Äôs first Artificial Intelligence platform for Blockchain built on top of Natural Language Understanding technology with the DApps marketplace.    What is all about?  Our mission: the creation of a strong AI (Artificial general intelligence) that will be open to all, controlled and trained by developers throughout the entire world.  The concept is similar to Elon Musk's OpenAI, but for meaning. We are developing a platform for analyzing large amounts of text data, solving the problems of extracting knowledge (IR ‚Äì information retrieval) and complex semantic classification based on machine learning, neural networks and deep learning technologies. Our priorities are the banking sector, biotechnology and medicine, security and law enforcement. The key element of the platform is a universal constructor for complex classifications of text, i.e. an AI designer.    We offer:  Dapps marketplace Whether you are a data scientist or businessman, you can make your own linguistic applications, sell them and make money.   Artificial Intelligence With GraphGrail's AI platform, by using Google Tensorflow and other tools, you can create and teach neural networks for complex classifications.  Smart contracts GraphGrail AI is the "brains" of a smart contract - a cross-blockchain service that uses webAPIs, datasources and analysis to automate contract execution.   Key problems we solve Tesla learns from cameras and GPS. In natural language all the data can be labeled by people only Not enough datasets What is the key problem in data-science and text mining? There simply aren't enough datasets with seven figure sample sizes (from thousand to million samples) to teach neural networks in many industries, including banking, telecom, media and government agencies. Even if the business does have such datasets, using machine learning to gather, clean and make training and test sets is extremely difficult and time consuming even for skilled data scientists. Training such as this can take between 5 and 10 months for a normal sized dataset, and even though we use neural networks and Deep Learning frameworks to simplify the task, it is a one time solution - every step must be repeated over and over again to keep your linguistic models up to date. That's why business truly needs GraphGrail AI. Smart contracts are not so "smart" as they could be   Smart contracts risks Smart contracts, by their nature, are able to run algorithmic calculations and store and retrieve data. Oracles fill this void by watching the blockchain (Ethereum, EOS, Bitshares) for events and responding to them by publishing the results of a query back to the contract. In this way, contracts can interact with the off-chain world. This introduces obvious trust problems. Another complex problem is to prove that smart contract conditions are executed in real world. Smart contracts can easily check the amount of a bank account, but real-world conditions like weather changes, companies' buy-sell events, political or legal decisions, contract details and force majeur events are much more complex. This is where GraphGrail AI comes in.   HOW IT WORKS Full stack data analysis solution GraphGrail AI is an all in one, full cycle solution. It offers all necessary data preparation tasks, including text parsing, cleaning, our AI designer for building linguistic models, testing facilities, machine learning and neural network tuning, and a decentralized app marketplace to make money with the platform. You will not need any other service. Case: smart-contracts  With GraphGrail AI, you can lower risks of implementing smart contacts in you business. Our technology offers convenient stack, including a data oracle, a trust gate to real-world data including social networks (Steemit, Golos.io, etc.), Wikipedia, and news resources. The smart contract can check conditions automatically, detecting weather changes, force-majeur circumstances or political risks, adding real agility to the smart contracts industry. Presale end date: until $10 000 reached or 25, July, 6 a.m. UTC. (5 days) 1 GGL price: $0.014 (- 30% from 0.02) - for early adopters. Cap for closed presale: $10 000. Cap in Ethereum: 55. Ethereum price is fixed every day on the level of btc-e.com exchange price in USD. Investors will receive GAI tokens starting from 21, July, 6 a.m. UTC.
